      "title": "Four hospitalised following clash at \u2019GotaGoGama\u2019",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four persons were hospitalized with cut injuries following a clash at GotaGoGama protest site at Galle Face Green early this morning.",
        "Hospital sources said the injured were aged between 17 and 20 years and are residents of Colombo 15 and Wellampitiya.",
        "At least 10 persons who were occupying Temple Trees were also injured in a clash yesterday."
      ],
